data.output: The man had quickly realised that he filled his tank with petrol instead of diesel when the engine cut out. Trying to pump it out of his tank was impossible as he had not tools to do so. He tried calling around to see if anyone had a means to fix his problem, but alas he has to call a local garage to pick him and his car up. He was hoping and praying that his car would be able to be fixed. It doesn't look good.

There was no stamp on the letter. It is being held at the local post office, waiting for jane to arrive and pay for the delivery. This annoyed jane, as she couldn't understand who would send one, let alone without a stamp on it.

The church's organ did not comply with health and safety standards. the pipes were close to falling off and were not screwed or bolted down to anything, they were just hanging loose. For a church which is part of such a big empire, surely they could be able to afford the proper installation of their own organ?

A plush of the pokemon gloom, which is one of my favourites, is so hard to come by nowadays that i would make a substatial payment to purchase one that exists. I would even travel the globe to aquire one. But alas, i believe that they stopped making them a while ago, so i will need to find an alternative source.
